National Bank of Canada May Expand, Make Acquisitions, CEO Vachon Says

-- B y   S e a n   B .   P a s t e r n a k
-- 
2011-03-29T13:54:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-29/national-bank-of-canada-may-expand-make-acquisitions-ceo-vachon-says.html
National Bank of Canada (NA) ’s will use
excess cash to invest in existing businesses and make
acquisitions before paying higher returns to shareholders, Chief
Executive Officer Louis Vachon said.  Vachon, speaking today at a conference in  Montreal 
sponsored by National Bank Financial, said  Canada ’s sixth-
largest bank may expand in Western Canada, Ontario and the
